 \"Asher-Smith\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith's last global individual medal was a bronze in 2022, and it is five years since her only world title.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Asher-Smith's last global individual medal\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"five years\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"her only world title\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite that, heptathlon great Ennis-Hill said: \\\"It's so, so tough in the sprints, and it's going to be a real challenge.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heptathlon great Ennis-Hill\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprints\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"a real challenge\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she came out at the beginning of the season right up there with the rest of the girls.\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's had a good winter, she's not had any particular niggles and she's consistently built for Paris, so I think she can be right up there in the medals, definitely.\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999763531, \"rank\": 2.3734614331316114e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good winter\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"any particular niggles\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She knows it's not an easy challenge, she knows the field for both the 100 and 200 will be absolutely phenomenal.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an easy challenge\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she's also got the talent to do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the talent\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith has been the leading light of the British team in the past, but looks likely to be usurped in Paris by Keely Hodgkinson, arguably Britain's best bet for an athletics gold.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.854469195859686, \"rank\": 0.0972222540649021, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999763531, \"rank\": 2.3734614331316114e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1584, \"end\": 1600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Asher-Smith\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"the leading light\", \"from\"